(a,b)
y=\frac ba x
x^n+\left(\frac ba x\right)^n=1
x^n= \frac 1{1+(\frac ba)^n}=\frac {a^n}{a^n+b^n}, x=\left(\frac {a^n}{a^n+b^n}\right)^{\frac 1n}
x^n+y^n=1
(x(\theta),y(\theta)) = (\cos^{2/n}\theta,\sin^{2/n}\theta)
(x_*,y_*)
(x_*,y_*)=(r\cos\phi,r\sin\phi)
\theta=\phi
n=2
 D(x,y,\lambda) = (x-x_*)^2 + (y-y_*)^2+ 2\lambda \big(x^n+y^n-1\big) . 
